Class FQAN

java.lang.Object
  org.glite.voms.FQAN

public class FQAN
extends Object

Parses and assembles Fully Qualified Attribute Names (FQANs) used by VOMS. FQANs are defined as
<group>[/Role=[<role>][/Capability=<capability>]]
